<!-- constructor Visibility: public -->
<element name="TTokenizer.Create">
<short>Constructor for the class.</short>
<descr>
Converts a string into a list of tokens. The caller is reponsible for providing
a TStringList that will be used to hold the tokens and managing the memory associated
with the TStringList, including freeing it when it is no longer needed.
<p>Parameters:</p>
<ul>
<li>InputString - The string that will be split into tokens.</li>
<li>TokenList - The TStringList that will be used to store the tokens. The caller
is responsible for managing the memory associated with this TStringList.</li>
</ul>
</descr>
